cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SI, cs.CV 

This paper involves the development of a tool that crafts adversarial samples to evade AdGraph, a learning-based adblocker. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also involves the use of machine learning, which suggests categories such as cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also deals with web applications, which suggests categories such as cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) and cs.CV (Computer Vision).
